 Purpose:
Blog & Load

Access Information:
- URL: http://blog.lab.local
- Location (VM): apps.lab.local
- Container/Service Name: wordpress (Docker container)

Credentials:
- Admin Username: admin
- Admin Password Location: [stored in ansible vault]

Technical Details:
- Database: mariaDB
- Configuration Files: /opt/docker/docker-compose.yml
- Data Location: /opt/docker/wordpress/wp-config-docker.php
- Log Location: /opt/docker/wordpress/debug.log

Common Operations:

Restart:
docker compose wordpress

View Logs:
docker logs | grep wordpress

Check Status:
docker ps | grep gitea

Backup:
docker exec mariadb mysqldump -u root -pPASSWORD wordpress > /opt/backups/wordpress-db-$(date +%Y%m%d).sql
tar -czf /opt/backups/wordpress-files-$(date +%Y%m%d).tar.gz /opt/docker/wordpress/

Dependencies:
- Requires: MariaDB, FreeIPA
- Required by: n/a

